IMPORTANT ABOUT LGPL-3.0 DEPENDENCIES:
---------------------------------------

All 8 packages with LGPL-3.0-or-later license are optional native modules 
of the sharp library (@img/sharp-*). They are used only during the build 
process for image optimization and are NOT included in the final product 
(_site/). Therefore, they are compatible with commercial use, as they are 
not part of the distributed product.

